						<h1>Air purifier brand to choose the right, don't choose</h1>
					</div>
					<div class="airclear"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="news-article pb20">
						<img class="airw" src="images/news1.jpg">
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						Much affected by the cold windy weather, a cooling, troubled days of fog haze dispersed by a blow, recently hit by cooling the air purifier. To choose a suitable air purifier, but the types of air purifier brand on the market is too much, it made the choice is difficult, as long as the understanding of the main approach to purify air purifiers on the market, then according to the using demand will know how to select the air purifier, air purifier which brand is good.
					</p>
					<h2>The purification of the air purifier</h2>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						Passive, active, composite of three methods for purification, while others, such as static, negative ions, ozone, photocatalytic, uv, etc. The use of the technology is mature in the field of air purification. Passive way of purification is the mesh filter, filter is the most important HEPA and activated carbon filter, the market is the most common composite filter purifier, is also the best purification way, on behalf of the brand and Wallace CM3075, mesh filter purification, passive combined with catalyst, ultraviolet light, negative ions, such as active way of purification, purifying indoor pollution, particles and peculiar smell effect is more outstanding, thoroughly.
					</p>
					<div class="text-center">
						<img src="images/article1.jpg">
					</div>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						Here mainly introduce negative ions and uv purification technology, negative ion air purifier have purification, dust removal, remove odor, sterilization effect, not need to change the filter regularly as filter type, and no noise; Ultraviolet air purifier can to purify of germs, bacteria and harmful microorganisms, prevent all kinds of infectious diseases.
					</p>
					<h2>Choose the right type of air purifie </h2>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						Air purifier national standards to be announced next year, the air purifier is the most important indicator of CADR, namely clean air volume is not allow to ignore, the numerical directly decide the size of the purification efficiency of air purifier. For example, a capacity of 400 air purifier, clean air to purify in 1 hour 90% of particulate matter, it can only be used within 42 cubic volume of the room. Assume that the room is 3 meters high, the use of area is 56 square meters. Now, however, there are also many products directly indicate the coverage area, because of the purifier in each room move easily, so, as long as you select the products that meet the biggest room in the home area.
					</p>
					<h2>The following circumstances, should choose and buy air purifier products </h2>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						1, the newly decorated house. Decorate material more or less will produce some pollution, increase indoor formaldehyde, benzene and other harmful substances, at this point, just need a can in addition to the harmful gas such as formaldehyde air purifier to help. Want to remind is, however, it is a good cleaner than vapour that open a window, also don't point.
					</p>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						2, the bedroom. For many workers, the bedroom is in a day, stay for the longest room at home. If don't have enough time or conditions of ventilation during the day, the house of the air quality. So, best can put an air purifier in the bedroom, as far as possible to family members to provide a fresh air environment of sleep.
					</p>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						3, children, pregnant women, the elderly or patients with respiratory disease's room. The above four kind of person is a high-risk population of PM2.5 pollution hazards, for their room, pollution prevention and control work must be done.
					</p>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						4, severe fog area. Haze in the region is more serious, and frequent outdoor PM2.5 index table, many families thought that as long as you close the window, indoor is not pollution, but closed doors and Windows, indoor harmful gas such as more bacteria and odor, suggest install fresh air system or buy air purifier products, purification of indoor air.
					</p>
					<p class="newsdes airtext">
						If in a fog more serious area, at the same time, family and children, the elderly, consider composite filter, in this recommendation and Max CM3075 this purifier, in addition to basic HEPA, activated carbon filter to remove indoor particles, the harmful gas such as formaldehyde, benzene, and ultraviolet ray, negative ion can sterilization, dust, and other functions; Numerical display real-time monitoring of indoor air quality, the remote control remote control is suitable for pregnant women, the elderly, not convenient to use the crowd; Sleep patterns, open in the night, will not affect the adult and the child rest; Time switch machine can use flexible setting time; Unique child protection function, but also to protect children from harm.
					</p>
